  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Borneo rescue centre to purchase land</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We are looking to purchase land in Malaysian Borneo. This will allow us to rehabilitate degraded land to grow food for the rescue centre&apos;s numerous endangered species including orangutans, gibbons, sun bears and clouded leopards. The illegal pet trade has meant that numerous animals need to be rescued and there are more coming in all the time. Feeding them is expensive so by purchasing our own land we can employ local people to grow sustainable food and reduce our running costs significantly.</narrative>
  </description>
